Params: {2: 'Nanami', 3: "Is, is it all because of Nanami...? The virus... it's spreading and turning the entire city into hell.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Mommy and Daddy have become so strange...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "Mimi's running around biting things like mad. And Mommy and Daddy kept arguing.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Nanami can only hug them as hard as she can and tell them to not be afraid. Nanami, Nanami will protect everyone...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Can you not glare at Nanami... with that expression...?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "Nanami's head... hurts so much lately... Mommy... Nanami's hurt...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "But... I don't know since when... Mommy's disappeared.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "It's dangerous outside... Nanami... will have to find Mommy.", 4: '1'}
